Subject: [PATCH 15/22] =?UTF-8?q?fix:=20bail=20on=20optParam/autoParam=20f?=
 =?UTF-8?q?ields=20=E2=80=94=20kernel=20keeps=20wrappers=20in=20rec=20mino?=
 =?UTF-8?q?r=20premise=20(failsafe=20caught=20the=20drift)?=
